channel.title: Help?
channel.description:
Hey,
i got my server online but it still comes under the name of stealthzscape when its online for example it says 'welcome to stealthscape'. Does anyone know how to change this to the name of my server?

item.title: Help?
item.dc:creator: @recker450 recker450
item.description:
@recker450 wrote:

goto client.java
ctrl + f
find stealthscape
replace it to your server name
and then close and save
and compile
